# Refresh the license truth file every 15 minutes.
# license_check.py reads /etc/cctv-license.conf (BASE_URL + DEVICE_ID + TOKEN,
# written by nvrd-core on link/resync) → calls the cloud → writes
# /var/run/cctv-license-state, which nvrd-core reads to drive the licensed
# (Active) state. Requires python3-openssl (stdlib ssl) in the image.
# Without this cron the truth file is only produced on a manual resync and
# never refreshed, so entitlement drifts to stale/fail-open.
*/15 * * * * /srv/cctv/scripts/license_check.py >/dev/null 2>&1
